'''Cryptberries''' were [[Poison/Legends|poisonous]] [[Fruit/Legends|fruits]] whose venom was [[Death/Legends|lethal]] to most [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Species/Legends|species]]. They were primarily found in and around the graveyards on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Necropolis (Core Worlds)|Necropolis]]. [[Zak Arranda/Legends|Zak Arranda]] was knocked unconscious by a diluted cryptberry.

